esting properties in phase transitions from the\nviewpoint of entropy surface density, or equivalently from the viewpoint of a\nsingle black hole molecule entropy, for the five-dimensional neutral\nGauss-Bonnet AdS black hole.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 11 Mar 2021 13:45:31 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 27 Mar 2021 10:34:16 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-03-30"}
