rovides real-time safety and operational instructions\nand insights for structural health monitoring (SHM) purposes, allowing\nprevention of environmental damage, and loss of human lives.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 11 Mar 2021 13:57:08 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 5 Apr 2021 17:19:16 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-04-06"}
